click 'My Views' link from side menu
Click to create a new View
Click on the User drop down menu on the Header
Click on the 'Configure' link from user drop down menu on the header page
Enter view name to Default View field
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Get a page form the 'Dashboard' drop-down menu
